### 

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/notes


### get all notes

GET {{baseUrl}} HTTP/1.1


### get note

GET {{baseUrl}}/1 HTTP/1.1


### delete note

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1 HTTP/1.1


### create note

POST {{baseUrl}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "kulala is great for testing API",
  "important": true
}
